All Classes

Class Summary 
Class Description
FileManager
Loads the initial tool and supplier datasets into the application, handing over an instantiated Shop class to the front-end.
Inventory
Holds an array list of the tools that the tool shop currently holds in the inventory.
Order
Holds the data for each daily order, including an arraylist of orderlines for each tool that has been ordered.
OrderLine
Stores the individual tool order data, and handles tool quantity updates after additional stock has been ordered.
OrderRepository
Holds a list of all of the daily orders that have been made through time.
Shop
Stores objects for the supplier list, inventory, and order repository.
Supplier
Stores the data for each individual supplier.
SupplierList
Stores the supplier list information for the store.
Tool
Holds the data for a single tool in the shop's inventory.
ToolStoreApp
Displays the user interface to the console, and allows for user interaction with the application.
